{"tid":2419853,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"駐港解放軍親自指導　懲教海關逐步引入中式「鵝步」","createTime":"2021-02-23T14:12:53.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-24T07:03:26.000Z","uid":20933,"like":63,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":59,"replies":[{"pid":"7d894b9557db2962a54eb2993a15c05ca03df432","tid":2419853,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T14:12:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Kb2L1Am7YUuG6UFpDsic_CcQf4E=/720x405/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/AD7YBWFNTZEB3AXNSDYRIETZ3E.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FKb2L1Am7YUuG6UFpDsic_CcQf4E%3D%2F720x405%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FAD7YBWFNTZEB3AXNSDYRIETZ3E.jpg&h=044fc341&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有指解放軍駐港部隊由昨日（22日）起，派出10名駐港部隊三軍儀仗隊官兵到黄竹坑警察學院，向警隊、入境處等各大紀律部隊教授中式步操，為期兩星期，多名紀律部隊首長承認有派員到警察學院受訓，其中懲教署、海關稱會分階段引入中式步操。懲教署署長胡英明更稱希望學習中式步操，「我想㗎，我想㗎，因為我鍾意學新嘢」。<br />\n<br />\n各大紀律部隊首長今日被傳媒問到有否派員參與訓練，全部首長承認有派員參與，懲教署、海關稱會分階段引入中式步操；而警務處、消防處則指現階段未有轉用中式步操的計劃。本港五大紀律部隊現時仍沿用英式步操，日後會否全面轉用中式步操，各大紀律部隊首長均沒有明確回應。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210223/WPF3IH7HQZGRTBJ4C3OPFR52AQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210223%2FWPF3IH7HQZGRTBJ4C3OPFR52AQ%2F&d=w4lkeVluhl8nqpRa%2FCUv35Khd8YmQljH21R%2F5cbT5WU%3D&h=4968b1d5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210223%2FWPF3IH7HQZGRTBJ4C3OPFR52AQ%2F&h=fc942f33\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210223/WPF3IH7HQZGRTBJ4C3OPFR52AQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/CLowJ8GHH_w/?igshid=3k0oz3bcnmix\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCLowJ8GHH_w%2F%3Figshid%3D3k0oz3bcnmix&d=w4lkeVluhl8nqpRa%2FCUv35Khd8YmQljH21R%2F5cbT5WU%3D&h=d365fb33\" data-ef-url=\"https://emb